Arcangel/Fury/Silverbolt



Arcangel waits for Blade Runner to be reprogramed he noticed that his foot 
had been hit by a missle. Someone from the alliance base must have shot at 
him.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

[I was about to post damage for Fury anyways]

Fury gets hit by three of the missles and his thrown backwards. but 
Silverbolt catches him.


Fury: thanks

Silverbolt: it was my duty

Fury: right



Silverbolt walks over and picks up skar blaise and they start to fly back to 
base with him.

fury turns back to beast mode but his chest is still in great pain form the 
missles.
